<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Chromebook on Torwald Log</title><link>https://torwald-sergesson.github.io/tags/chromebook/</link><description>Recent content in Chromebook on Torwald Log</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://torwald-sergesson.github.io/tags/chromebook/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Make Chromebook Super_L key Control</title><link>https://torwald-sergesson.github.io/blog/2024/xmodmap-chromebook/</link><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://torwald-sergesson.github.io/blog/2024/xmodmap-chromebook/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;âžœ ~ xmodmap
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;xmodmap: up to &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt; keys per modifier, &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;keycodes in parentheses&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;shift Shift_L &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0x32&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;, Shift_R &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0x3e&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;lock Caps_Lock &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0x42&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;control Control_L &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0x25&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;, Control_R &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0x69&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mod1 Alt_L &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0x40&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;, Alt_R &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0x6c&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;, Meta_L &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0xcd&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mod2 Num_Lock &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0x4d&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mod3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mod4 Super_L &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0x85&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;, Super_L &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0xce&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;, Hyper_L &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0xcf&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mod5 ISO_Level3_Shift &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0x5c&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;, Mode_switch &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0xcb&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Copy current xmodmap config:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;xmodmap -pke &amp;gt; ~/.xmodmap
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Do its backup just in case&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cp ~/.xmodmap ~/.xmodmap.bak
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Drop &lt;code&gt;Super_L&lt;/code&gt; from &lt;code&gt;mod4&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;xmodmap -e &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;remove mod4 = Super_L&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;And add it to Control:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;xmodmap -e &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;add Control = Super_L&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;As a result:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>